1- Install Terraform on Ubuntu, following steps from terraform documentations
2- Creating an AWS user with EC2 privilige
3- Install AWS CLI on ubuntu:

curl "https://awscli.amazonaws.com/awscli-exe-linux-x86_64.zip" -o "awscliv2.zip"
unzip awscliv2.zip
sudo ./aws/install

4- Configure the AWS credentials through the CLI by adding the new user details:

aws configure


